name: UOB ATM - Esplanade MRT Circle Line Station

reviews.text: Not the most straightforward ATM to find, but if you're around the South Beach area, and looking for a UOB ATM, there's one en route from Suntec City to Esplanade MRT station. It's right by 7 Eleven, hidden in a small alley, together with the few other ATM Machines and SAM machine.

vicinity: No. 90 Bras Basah Road, MRT Station
